你如果讲负债，Obama期间除了第一年经济危机大规模政府赤字，后面一直是在削减赤字 <a href="https://datalab.usaspending.gov/americas-finance-guide/deficit/trends/" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">https://datalab.usaspending.gov/americas-finance-guide/deficit/trends/</a>
